Consts.useLimit: Election results are those certified by the State Canvassing Board. Election statistics are those certified by County Canvassing Boards and reported to the Office of the Secretary of State. Office of the Minnesota Secretary of State maintains this boundary data as accurately as possible, but cannot assure 100% accuracy. For definitive precinct lines, please contact the jurisdiction (city, township, or county for unorganized territory) in question. To check precinct and districts or find polling place for an address, use the Secretary of State's Polling Place Finder: http://pollfinder.sos.state.mn.us. Municipal boundaries derived from 6/19/2012 CTU Boundaries dataset from MnGeo and U.S. Census redistricting data. Precinct boundaries created and updated using reference from NCompass, Mn/DOT, and TIGER road data, MN DNR lake and stream data, MN DNR PLSS QQ data, imagery served by MnGeo, and select data from OpenStreetMap. Includes election district boundary adjustments made under MS 2.91, subd. 2 and MS 204B.146, subd. 3. Updated for boundary adjustments (annexation, detachment, incorporation, dissolution) approved by Municipal Boundary Adjustment Unit of the Office of Administrative Hearings, including those prior to October 14, 2014.
